ref:_00D7091pB._500Q000D09jl:ref

We are all set on this, the key length was the issue, we had incorrectly set the RSA key to only 1024 bits when manually generating the key.  All of our other appliances/VMs generate CSRs thru their UIs so this was a bit of an unusual procedure for us.
